Lemma opp_prod : forall O E E' ME X MX, Opp O E E' E ME -> Opp O E E' X MX -> Prod O E E' X ME MX.

Lemma diff_of_squares : forall O E E' A B A2 B2 A2MB2 APB AMB F, Prod O E E' A A A2 -> Prod O E E' B B B2 -> Diff O E E' A2 B2 A2MB2 -> Sum O E E' A B APB -> Diff O E E' A B AMB -> Prod O E E' APB AMB F -> A2MB2 = F.

assert (HNC : ~ Col O E E') by (apply diff_ar2 in HA2MB2; unfold Ar2 in *; spliter; Col).
